{"TopicId":200840,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"How do you make KSP full screen on computer?","CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:09:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:09:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you make KSP full screen on computer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:23:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the main settings menu:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wsUu8oe.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002249.78\u0022 height=\u0022224\u0022 width=\u0022450\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wsUu8oe.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:32:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223937330\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200840\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615159391\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196199\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022VoidSquid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, VoidSquid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the main settings menu:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think thats not a true FullScreen, its still a\u00A0Windowed Fullscreen,\u00A0if you google there must be a fix to add a launch parameter to go really full.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf thats what Dr. Kerbal is asking, although from some search i did its like a Unity thing, maybe i am wrong.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-03-07T23:35:04Z\u0022 title=\u002203/07/2021 11:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 7, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Boyster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dr. Kerbal","CreatedById":207217,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:38:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223937330\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200840\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615159391\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196199\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022VoidSquid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 minutes ago, VoidSquid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the main settings menu:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wsUu8oe.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wsUu8oe.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002249.78\u0022 height=\u0022224\u0022 width=\u0022450\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wsUu8oe.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you. And I also leanred you can use Alt\u002BEnter to go full screen to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidSquid","CreatedById":196199,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-03-07T23:39:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs per my experience it is actually a true full screen. For example, to have the chat displayed via a widget as an overlay while streaming, one needs to disable the full screen\u00A0radio button.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223937335\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200840\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221615160319\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207217\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dr. Kerbal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Dr. Kerbal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I also leanred you can use Alt\u002BEnter to go full screen to\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, the classic\u00A0Windows key board command, which proves my last post.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}